He's got the second-best rating out of 50 governors.
Hogan doesn't react easily to heat.
He's led the state steadfastly and firmly on principle.
He has also skillfully used Facebook as his primary channel of communication with his constituents, posting a photo of his bald head in chemotherapy.
The governor's Facebook page is a public and official forum, maintained by his staff with taxpayer funds, and therefore blocking users from visiting it is unnecessary and even dangerous.
